However, in response to the limitation period defence raised by this motion for summary judgement, the plaintiff has invoked one argument: the doctrine of promissory estoppel. Mindful of each party's duty to put its best case forward (
 <FRAGMENT_SUPPRESSED> FTR 231 [
Riva
];
 <FRAGMENT_SUPPRESSED> [2008] FCJ 1210), I have carefully reviewed the evidence and jurisprudence submitted by the plaintiff in support of its estoppel argument.
